text: Gollaprolu Mandal is one of the 64 mandals in East Godavari District of Andhra Pradesh. As per census 2011, there are 10 villages. == Demographics == Gollaprolu Mandal has total population of 78,926 as per the Census 2011 out of which 39,773 are males while 39,153 are females and the average Sex Ratio of Gollaprolu Mandal is 984. The total literacy rate of Gollaprolu Mandal is 61.97%.
